::Magmatron::

    "Yes, I was just talking to Unicron, that would account for my change of 
body,"  Magmatron explained. Magmatron looked past Shredder to the far wall. 
He walked over and seemingly started to talk to the wall.
    "Hello, Phobia. Guess who's back." Magmatron said to one of the spider 
bots climbing the wall. He turned back to Shredder and once again walked to 
him, his wings flowing behind him like a dark knights cape. (Batman reference)
